<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Email Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo span {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #3D4F58;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #3D4F58;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .verification-code {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="logo">
    <span>VTribe</span>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>OTP Request</h1>
    <p>Dear user,</p>
    <p>Here is the OTP you requested for</p>
    <div class="verification-code">
      <%= verificationCode %>
    </div>
    <p>Take note that this OTP will expire in the next 10m</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The VTribe Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
